videos.description: Q1 (7:23) UCF Ashley Polacek makes nice back-cut, finishes with Layup. Assisted by Aliyah Gregory.
videos.headline: A. Polacek makes nice back-cut, finishes with Layup. Assisted by A. Gregory.

videos.description: Q1 (6:52) CONN Katie Lou Samuelson Steal. She sends it to Kia Nurse who finishes with a layup and gets the foul call.
videos.headline: K. Samuelson Steal. She sends it to K. Nurse who finishes with a layup and gets the foul call.

videos.description: Q1 (5:30) UCF Aliyah Gregory made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Zykira Lewis.
videos.headline: A. Gregory made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Z. Lewis.

videos.description: Q1 (5:06) CONN Gabby Williams steals the ball before UCF even makes it past halfcourt, easily runs it back for the layup.
videos.headline: G. Williams steals the ball before UCF even makes it past halfcourt, easily runs it back for the layup.

videos.description: Q1 (2:45) CONN Gabby Williams gets fouled and makes Layup. Assisted by Breanna Stewart.
videos.headline: G. Williams gets fouled and makes Layup. Assisted by B. Stewart.

videos.description: Q1 (0:33) CONN Napheesa Collier made Layup. Good patience on the bullet pass down low from Kia Nurse.
videos.headline: N. Collier made Layup. Good patience on the bullet pass down low from K. Nurse.

videos.description: Gabby Williams limping off the court as she gets subbed out with 2 minutes remaining in the first quarter.
videos.headline: G. Williams limping off the court as she gets subbed out with 2 minutes remaining in the first quarter.

videos.description: Q2 (8:20) CONN Napheesa Collier made nice up and under move to finish Layup. Assisted by Kia Nurse.
videos.headline: N. Collier made nice up and under move to finish Layup. Assisted by K. Nurse.

videos.description: Q2 (6:00) CONN Natalie Butler made put-back Jumper.
videos.headline: N. Butler made put-back Jumper.

videos.description: Q2 (5:26) CONN Kia Nurse battles on the ground, takes a hand to the face to win back possession for the huskies.
videos.headline: K. Nurse battles on the ground, takes a hand to the face to win back possession for the huskies.

videos.description: Q2 (4:23) UCF Kayla Thigpen steal, takes it down for a Layup.
videos.headline: K. Thigpen steal, takes it down for a Layup.

videos.description: Q2 (2:40) CONN Nice rebound by Katie Lou Samuelson,avoids fouling. Sends it down court to Moriah Jefferson who finishes with a Layup.
videos.headline: Nice rebound by K. Samuelson, avoids fouling. Sends it down court to M. Jefferson who finishes with a Layup.

videos.description: Q2 (0:04) CONN Natalie Butler gets the offensive rebound, battles through to finish with a left-handed Layup at the conclusion of the first half.
videos.headline: N. Butler gets the offensive rebound, battles through to finish with a left-handed Layup at the conclusion of the first half.

videos.description: Q3 (9:43) CONN Moriah Jefferson starts off the second half with a steal, beating out her defender downcourt for a layup.
videos.headline: M. Jefferson starts off the second half with a steal, beating out her defender downcourt for a layup.

videos.description: Q3 (7:49) CONN Katie Lou Samuelson has a huge smile on her face after making a nice cut down low and finshing with a layup. Assisted by Gabby Williams.
videos.headline: K. Samuelson has a huge smile on her face after making a nice cut down low and finshing with a layup. Assisted by G. Williams.

videos.headline: K. Samuelson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by M. Jefferson.

videos.description: Q4 (3:13) CONN Courtney Ekmark makes a european move around the defenders to finish her layup. For the fourth time this year, and the second game in a row, UCONN has reached 100 points.
videos.headline: C. Ekmark makes a european move around the defenders to finish her layup. For the fourth time this year, and the second game in a row, UCONN has reached 100 points.
